# GrowthWave Multi-Domain Redirects
# =================================
# Routes each custom domain to its respective brand section.
# Place this file in the /public directory so it's copied to /dist on build.

# GrowthWave Advisors (parent brand)
https://growthwaveadvisors.com/*  /advisors/:splat  200
https://www.growthwaveadvisors.com/*  /advisors/:splat  200

# GrowthWave Capital
https://growthwavecapital.com/*  /capital/:splat  200
https://www.growthwavecapital.com/*  /capital/:splat  200

# GrowthWave Properties
https://growthwaveproperties.com/*  /properties/:splat  200
https://www.growthwaveproperties.com/*  /properties/:splat  200

# Handle root paths explicitly (ensures homepage works)
https://growthwaveadvisors.com/  /advisors/  200
https://growthwavecapital.com/  /capital/  200
https://growthwaveproperties.com/  /properties/  200
